==English==
===Adjective===
'''historic'''
# having [[importance]] or [[significance]] in [[history]]
# belonging to the [[past]]; [[historical]]

===Note===

Sentences involving the word "historic" sometimes use "a historic" and sometimes use "an historic".  This has something to do with British English versus American English, and should be expanded in this article.

